1 导言

一般数据处理的过程:

2 准备工作

2.1 安装R和RStudio

  • R语言官网(下载安装软件): https://www.r-project.org/

  • RStudio Desktop下载: https://www.rstudio.com/products/rstudio/download/

2.2 RStudio工作环境

2.3 安装加载程序包

选择CRAN: Tools -> Global Options -> Packages

install.packages("tidyverse")
library(tidyverse)

install.packages("gapminder")
library(gapminder)

2.4 改为当前工作目录

Session -> Set Working Directory -> To Source File Location

2.5 R Help: ?

在Console中键入 ? 安装包名/函数名, 例如?gapminder

2.6 几个有用的快捷键

  • 代码补全: Tab

  • 执行代码: Ctrl + Enter

  • 注释代码: Ctrl + Shift + C

  • 获取之前的命令: Ctrl + Up

  • 赋值运算(<-): Alt + -

  • Pipe运算: Ctrl + Shift + M

  • 修改快捷键: Tools -> Modify Keyboard Shortcuts...

3 读写数据

3.1 导入数据

CSV文件

gapminder1 <- read_csv("data/gapminder1.csv") 
## Parsed with column specification:
## cols(
##   country = col_character(),
##   continent = col_character(),
##   year = col_double(),
##   type = col_character(),
##   count = col_double()
## )
  • 变量名
gapminder1 <- read_csv("data/gapminder1.csv", col_names = FALSE) # no column name
gapminder1 <- read_csv("data/gapminder1.csv", col_names = c("country", "continent", "year", "variable", "value"), skip = 1) # change column names, skip the first row

Excel文件(.xls, .xlsx)

library(readxl)
gapminder1 <- read_excel("data/gapminder1.xlsx")
  • 读入特定spreadsheet数据
gapminder1 <- read_excel("data/gapminder1.xlsx", sheet = "gapminder1")

3.2 导出数据

write_csv(gapminder1, "data/gapminder.csv")

4.2.4 mutate: 增加新变量

mutate(gapminder,
    GDP = pop * gdpPercap,
    logpop = log(pop)
  )

#3 pipe运算
# x %>% f(y, ...)  :  f(x, y, ...)
# x %>% f(., y, ...): f(x, y , ...)
# x %>% f(y, .) : f(y, x)

gapminder %>% 
  distinct(country, continent) %>% 
  count(continent)

4.2.6 summerise: 描述性统计

计算平均寿命的均值与标准差

gapminder %>% 
  summarise(avg_lifeExp = mean(lifeExp), sd_lifeExp = sd(lifeExp))
## # A tibble: 1 x 2
##   avg_lifeExp sd_lifeExp
##         <dbl>      <dbl>
## 1        59.5       12.9

有用的函数:

  • Center: mean(), median()
  • Spread: sd(), IQR(), mad()
  • Range: min(), max(), quantile()
  • Position: first(), last(), nth()
  • Count: n(), n_distinct()
  • Logical: any(), all()

gapminder %>%

  arrange(gdpPercap, .by_group = TRUE) # .by_group=T 不可缺少, 否则arrange将无视group_by

  • 分组后filter&mutate

首先筛选观测值超过10个的国家, 然后计算这些国家人均GDP增长率

gapminder %>% 
  group_by(country) %>% 
  filter(n() > 10) %>% 
  mutate(
    gdp_growth = gdpPercap / lag(gdpPercap) - 1
  )

5.2 折线图: geom_line()

中国平均寿命的时间序列图

gapminder %>%
  filter(country == "China") %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = year, y = lifeExp)) + 
  geom_line(size = 1.2)

中国 v.s. 美国平均寿命

gapminder %>%
  filter((country == "China") | (country == "United States")) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = year, y = lifeExp, color = country)) + 
  geom_line(size = 1.2)

7 特别说明: 缺失值

7.1 缺失数据的表现形式

  • Explicit: 如NA
  • Implicit: 不存在的观测

7.2 R中如何表示缺失值?

NA: not available 缺失值

注意NAN不是缺失值: not a number 计算错误, 不是数值(比如, 除以0, log(负数)等). 一般出现NAN时, 需要检查计算过程.

7.3 如何处理缺失值?

7.3.1 找到缺失值

  • Explicit: is.na(), 返回数据集与原数据集大小相同, 元素为TRUE/FALSE

  • Implicit:
